150/mana per tick is another class myth...however 14 mana/tick for 2.5 hours is not a myth. <br>
<br>
 Without clarity almost every enounter in the game would not be possible...Its as important as slow/haste...When the game was designed clarity/slow/haste were building block enhacments Mod rods do not=them.<br>
